{"tid":2001644,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"星夢英皇歌手齊唱藍絲B哥哥作曲維穩廣東歌","createTime":"2020-05-04T16:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T02:19:58.000Z","uid":242050,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6345e025fa5693b59864ef3feb72749121a99e90","tid":2001644,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VBKx1q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VBKx1q.jpg&h=3ada6441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年反送中運動出現不少社運歌，《願榮光歸香港》無人不曉，連藍絲都要偷曲改歌撐警，不過政府3月實施限聚令，一個月之間由防疫措施，變成被警方濫用以驅趕香港人「和你唱」的萬能Key，黃絲們要重現往日大合唱的場面困難重重。<br />\n<br />\n選擇性執法下，黃絲唔唱得，藍絲以後有新歌唱，前特首董建華及梁振英最近籌組「香港再出發大聯盟」維穩。新組織成立了個幾星期，終於有動作，其YouTube專頁預告，明日（5日）朝早將會有主題曲《再出發》首播。雖然歌就未有得聽，但該條預告已經有歌曲班底、歌手、歌詞等資料，理所當然地見到自己友，包括<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>撐警鍾鎮濤負責作曲</strong></span></span>、簡嘉明填詞、葉澍暉編曲。預告亦有鳴謝英皇娛樂及星夢娛樂，所以主唱歌手方面都熟口熟面，包括<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">周柏豪、菊梓喬</span></strong></span>、無綫兩將<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鄭俊弘</span></span></strong>及<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">胡鴻鈞</span></strong></span>，英皇方面就派出<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">馬面雙妹嘜泳兒及許靖韻</span></strong></span>做代表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20200504/60903298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200504%2F60903298&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1qQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=7f4f0bb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200504%2F60903298&h=0311ad2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20200504/60903298</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6c963398bcdf1fea35f6a5ef54116b47d15de2","tid":2001644,"uid":242050,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"咪撚再同我講周柏豪係暗黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb25c58f0707621d62bcdee560a3007418a09fe","tid":2001644,"uid":209554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd37f683c236b08c60acf4031bfa7b7935922ec","tid":2001644,"uid":242050,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:21:20.000Z","msg":"驚喜的是，暫時未見蛋記派出資深文匯之友參與其中"},{"pid":"c685411a2bec7c3bbcc70603b6107db17e1aea28","tid":2001644,"uid":253223,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:22:11.000Z","msg":"負評搖撚準備<br />\n希望可以做到eason 蔡依琳個首咁樣一面倒dislike<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42f7c495c5f5054414592825f228eccdd58e99af","tid":2001644,"uid":242050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c685411a2bec7c3bbcc70603b6107db17e1aea28","tid":2001644,"uid":253223,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:22:11.000Z","msg":"負評搖撚準備<br />\n希望可以做到eason 蔡依琳個首咁樣一面倒dislike<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:23:16.000Z","msg":"Dislike師"},{"pid":"4e229e69738685a0c075e63aa635622602abba26","tid":2001644,"uid":246787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T16:24:56.000Z","msg":"妖 馬面許<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226a04c8c5ff174cead70ba9b922e720671e9f2d","tid":2001644,"uid":35191,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":